# 🤖 Internal AI Assistant Lite (Demo)
A lightweight conversational AI agent by Cyber Socialites that helps small 
teams with basic internal support — drafting emails, creating SOP steps, 
and answering general workplace questions.

## 🎯 Who It's For
Small teams and businesses looking for a no-fuss AI assistant for 
non-sensitive, everyday workplace tasks.

## ✨ Features
- Email drafting assistance
- Simple SOP step creation
- General workplace Q&A
- Lightweight and easy to use
- Designed for non-sensitive use cases

